<section class="section sr-prose">
  <div class="container--narrow">
    <h2 class="sr-prose__heading">Store Pickup Policy</h2>
    <p>You can choose to pick up your order at Menon Regenerative Institute for FREE. Your order will be ready to pick up within 1 business day after it was placed. You will receive a confirmation email, once your order is prepared for pickup.</p>
    <p>Please wait for a notification before picking up your order. Your order confirmation and ID will be needed for pickup.</p>
    <p>Pickup address:</p>
    <p>
      Menon Regenerative Institute<br />
      45 Essex Street, Suite 202<br />
      Millburn, NJ, 07041
    </p>
    <p>Opening Hours:</p>
    <p>
      Monday - Friday 10am - 6pm<br />
      Saturday 10am - 4pm
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .sr-prose__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);
    line-height: 1.25;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .sr-prose p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
  }

  .sr-prose p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
</style>
